# Web3Forms access key for the Contact form.
# Get a free key in seconds at https://web3forms.com (enter paddhu.xd96@gmail.com),
# then copy this file to `.env` and paste your key below — or hardcode it in
# src/config/site.ts (Web3Forms access keys are designed to be public/client-side).
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here

# Optional: override the base path (use "/" for a custom domain or Vercel).
# VITE_BASE=/portfolio-website/
